text: Torpedo Alley is a 1952 American World War II movie directed by Lew Landers and starring Mark Stevens, Charles Winninger, Dorothy Malone, Bill Williams, Douglas Kennedy, James Millican, William Henry, Charles Bronson. ==Other websites== * Category:1952 war movies Category:American war movies Category:World War II movies Category:Movies directed by Lew Landers
title: Torpedo Alley
